  "detailed_description": "Exo Wanderer is an indie game developed by a solo creator.<br><br>The story is set on Gliese 667Ce, 22 light-years away from Earth, where Earth’s civilization is in deep crisis. You can play as Du Hao or Zoey, one of the Exo Wanderers, or team up with a friend to control two characters on the same device. Each Exo Wanderer has their own unique tank. Explore this mysterious planet in hopes of finding a way to save Earth’s civilization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Local Co-op, Dual-Stick Combat</h2></li></ul>Play with a friend on the same screen, controlling two tanks to defeat all enemies and defend your base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Levels, Always Be Alert</h2></li></ul>Upgrade speed and turret levels through pickups, but beware—taking damage may cause downgrades, so stay alert to maintain your tank’s level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/bc5197d251a8bb769fe882c8a426075a.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Ammo Types, Combo Attacks</h2></li></ul>Collect various ammo through pickups, like fire or ice rounds, or even call in airstrikes. You can even launch a nuclear missile!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/3fca48c53fc6dae246a189579a4063b3.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shared Control, Two Become One</h2></li></ul>With two players, you can both control one tank—one drives, the other attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/f9fa4fea0605f7e98f5a7f575b887bb5.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deployable Turrets, Defend Your Base</h2></li></ul>Freely deploy turrets or obstacles to stop enemies from reaching your base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/cc73a40439834f48be1377355386697f.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galactic Blessings</h2></li></ul>Restore health with the Galactic Blessing, but be careful—choosing the wrong target could summon a meteor strike.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/bcb59efcd5f2d366968d0c3486e026d5.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quantum State, Supply Your Partner</h2></li></ul>If one player is destroyed, they enter Quantum State and can use elements to supply the remaining player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/50a6c9c30d9f3a4bb5f7d180ef5546f3.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Rich Variety of Enemies</h2></li></ul>With over 1,000 types of enemies, you'll also encounter mysterious and powerful foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/26a7d48cca1a5cd170b5546a9a60406a.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=253 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Equipment</h2></li></ul>Assemble or synthesize equipment using parts and particle energy fragments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nuclear Fusion, Elemental Synthesis</h2></li></ul>Use nuclear fusion to combine elements, crafting parts or particle energy fragments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-Player Mode</h2></li></ul>If you prefer a solo experience, you can enjoy 100% of the story and levels.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galactic History</h2></li></ul>Join Du Hao and Zoey as they uncover the mysteries of human civilization and the history of the galaxy.",
  "about_the_game": "Exo Wanderer is an indie game developed by a solo creator.<br><br>The story is set on Gliese 667Ce, 22 light-years away from Earth, where Earth’s civilization is in deep crisis. You can play as Du Hao or Zoey, one of the Exo Wanderers, or team up with a friend to control two characters on the same device. Each Exo Wanderer has their own unique tank. Explore this mysterious planet in hopes of finding a way to save Earth’s civilization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d53f60d72c953e83086019bbb685ffa.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Local Co-op, Dual-Stick Combat</h2></li></ul>Play with a friend on the same screen, controlling two tanks to defeat all enemies and defend your base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/7d9f0f587e337e35dd768ce297a64599.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Levels, Always Be Alert</h2></li></ul>Upgrade speed and turret levels through pickups, but beware—taking damage may cause downgrades, so stay alert to maintain your tank’s level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/bc5197d251a8bb769fe882c8a426075a.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Ammo Types, Combo Attacks</h2></li></ul>Collect various ammo through pickups, like fire or ice rounds, or even call in airstrikes. You can even launch a nuclear missile!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/3fca48c53fc6dae246a189579a4063b3.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shared Control, Two Become One</h2></li></ul>With two players, you can both control one tank—one drives, the other attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/f9fa4fea0605f7e98f5a7f575b887bb5.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deployable Turrets, Defend Your Base</h2></li></ul>Freely deploy turrets or obstacles to stop enemies from reaching your base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/cc73a40439834f48be1377355386697f.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galactic Blessings</h2></li></ul>Restore health with the Galactic Blessing, but be careful—choosing the wrong target could summon a meteor strike.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/bcb59efcd5f2d366968d0c3486e026d5.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quantum State, Supply Your Partner</h2></li></ul>If one player is destroyed, they enter Quantum State and can use elements to supply the remaining player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/50a6c9c30d9f3a4bb5f7d180ef5546f3.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=252 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Rich Variety of Enemies</h2></li></ul>With over 1,000 types of enemies, you'll also encounter mysterious and powerful foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/26a7d48cca1a5cd170b5546a9a60406a.avif?t=1732325610\" width=800 height=253 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Equipment</h2></li></ul>Assemble or synthesize equipment using parts and particle energy fragments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/4304869bae7592765862b8ed091c3385.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Nuclear Fusion, Elemental Synthesis</h2></li></ul>Use nuclear fusion to combine elements, crafting parts or particle energy fragments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1732325610\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.poster.avif?t=1732325610\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.webm?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208780/extras/c046b7646cd8e8b73ddbc0c594ae380e.mp4?t=1732325610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-Player Mode</h2></li></ul>If you prefer a solo experience, you can enjoy 100% of the story and levels.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galactic History</h2></li></ul>Join Du Hao and Zoey as they uncover the mysteries of human civilization and the history of the galaxy.",
